XC Trail Report

An android application for downloading and displaying xc ski trail reports.
This project is not affiliated with skinnyski.com, the Three Rivers Park District, or any website or trail manager.  Do not contact any website provider with questions or issues with this application.  All included reports are Copyright their respective site owners and subject to their terms of use.
This project is currently in beta, not all functionality may be completely implemented.  Please report issues on any problems you find.  Include the make/model and firmware revision of your phone.

